{"title":"RAAW Madonna V2.2 frame refined with improved force flow, more shock clearance","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/17/raaw-madonna-v2-2-frame-refined-with-improved-force-flow-more-shock-clearance/","date":1623924042000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Raaw mountain bikes have lifted the veil on the not-quite-third generation Madonna, the so-called V2.2. Maintaining the geometry of the V2 (if it’s not broken, why fix it), Raaw have refined the frame design to improve force flow throughout the suspension linkage and improve hardware tolerances. Here’s the what and why regarding the Raaw Madonna V2.2, but first…</p><p>The magnificent sound of a bike just… working. Praise be.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/X-qVZQcjmFQ?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.3918886155507346\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 complete bike with ohlins coil shock\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike-800x533.jpg 800w