ikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111553/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-complete-bike-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Raaw have redesigned the Madonna around an improved seat tube. The now single-piece hydroformed aluminium tube is designed to create a large intersection to the main pivot and rocker pivot with a reduced, but carefully defined, number of welds. This is said to increase strength while helping to distribute stress more evenly. For that reason, Raaw have been able to reduce the wall thickness thereby saving a little weight.</p><figure id=\"attachment_262075\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262075\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-single-piece-design.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-single-piece-design.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 redesigned around single piece hydroformed aluminium seat tube lighter stronger\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-single-piece-design.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-single-piece-design-200x300.jpg 200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-single-piece-design-800x1200.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111605/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-new-seat-tube-