aws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111548/raaw-madonna-new-lower-shock-mount-cnc-machined-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111548/raaw-madonna-new-lower-shock-mount-cnc-machined-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111548/raaw-madonna-new-lower-shock-mount-cnc-machined-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111548/raaw-madonna-new-lower-shock-mount-cnc-machined-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The lower shock mount now consists of two separate parts attached to the CNC machined interface on the bottom bracket. Raaw say this guarantees a very defined flow of stress from the shock into the frame. It also improves the tolerances and fit of the shock hardware, much like the brake mount on the non-driveside seat stay does.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 rocker link housed bearings\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111612/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-rocker-link-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The rocker link has been reworked such that the new rocker pivot design sees the bearings move from the main frame into the rocker link. The new pivot also reduces some of the complexity from the main frame, and is said to improve force flow from the rocker link into the seat tube, reducing the potential for noises that can occur after long periods of use.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 geometry chart\" width=\"1200\" height=\"786\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-297x195.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-800x524.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-768x503.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-696x456.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-1068x700.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-641x420.jpg 641w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-741x486.jpg 741w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-297x195.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-800x524.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-768x503.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-696x456.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-1068x700.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-641x420.jpg 641w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16102705/raaw-madonna-v2-point-2-frame-geometry-741x486.jpg 741w\"></a></p><h3>New Thru-Axle</h3><figure id=\"attachment_262081\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262081\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 thru-axle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"803\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-297x199.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-800x535.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-768x514.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-696x466.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-1068x715.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-628x420.jpg 628w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-297x199.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-800x535.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-768x514.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-696x466.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-1068x715.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111642/raaw-madonna-v22-thru-axle-628x420.jpg 628w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262081\">The axle comes standard with a nut that uses a 6 mm Allen key as well as a 15 mm socket. There is also a slimmer and lighter version with just the 15 mm socket interface.</figcaption></figure><p>Also new for the Madonna V2.2 (and available for the V2 and Jibb frames) is a new thru-axle system. It is designed to create a more rigid connection between the two dropouts, locking the left and right seatstays into place, resisting rotation and bending. It should also stop the axle from undoing while you’re riding.</p><h3>Madonna V2.2 (and all frames sold since 2017) get five year warranty</h3><figure id=\"attachment_251863\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251863\"><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON.jpg\" alt=\"RAAW JIBB SNOWY SCENE FULL BIKE SHOT FINLAY ANDERSON\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/RAAW_JIBB-SNOW-SHOOT-FINALY-ANDERSON-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251863\">The five year warranty extends to Raaw’s shorter travel mountain bike; the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/23/all-new-raaw-jibb-mid-travel-29er-trail-bike-looks-primed-for-throwing-shapes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jibb</a>. Credit: Finlay Anderson.</figcaption></figure><p>Raaw mountain bikes have now extended their frame warranty to five years, which extends to both the original and second owners. Not only does it apply to the new Madonna V2.2, it also covers all Raaw frames sold since 2017 (<em>i.e.</em> the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/23/all-new-raaw-jibb-mid-travel-29er-trail-bike-looks-primed-for-throwing-shapes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jibb</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2017/10/24/get-raaw-with-160mm-of-the-new-madonna-of-enduro-mountain-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Madonna V1</a> &amp; V2).</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111618/raaw-madonna-v22-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Due to the absolute state of parts availability across the industry, Raaw are holding off on selling full bikes. So, it’s frame and shock only, for the time being. The frameset including thru-axle, seat clamp and protective film retails at 2,390 € incl. VAT (that’s 2,008 € outside the EU). Shock options from Fox and Öhlins are available as well as Acros headsets.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp.jpg\" alt=\"raaw madonna v2.2 action shot corner shralp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111630/raaw-madonna-v22-shralp.jpg 1200w,https://bi