/bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/16111636/raaw-madonna-v22-step-down-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Want your V2.2 earlier? For an additional 125 €, Raaw are offering keen customers express delivery. This will secure you an air freighted frame, reducing the shipping time to Germany<br>down to two weeks. The express delivery comes on top of the regular shipping and is available until Sunday June 20th 23:59 CET.</p><p><a href=\"https://raawmtb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>raawmtb.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0dffadbdec924405427183738c62fee34530f40b1f64c87eda19e92b06c70308","category":"Cycling"}